fr.skyost.skyowallet.sync.synchronizer

Class SkyowalletSynchronizer<T extends EconomyObject>

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.skyost.skyowallet.sync.synchronizer.SkyowalletSynchronizer<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The object type.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SkyowalletAccountSynchronizer, SkyowalletBankSynchronizer

    public abstract class SkyowalletSynchronizer<T extends EconomyObject>
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a synchronizer that allows to synchronize a certain type of objects.
